ds/2024/10/billie-eilish-kamala-harris@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-kamala-harris@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-kamala-harris@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-kamala-harris@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/billie-eilish-kamala-harris@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>加大了对美国总统候选人<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris)</a>的支持，称哈里斯当选将使她“作为一名女性在我的国家感到安全”——看看下面这位歌手还说了什么。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="543" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826"><b>Billie Eilish – 《Hit Me Hard and Soft》评论：大胆、精彩、明亮</b></a></li></ul><p>9月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-and-finneas-endorse-kamala-harris-for-president-vote-like-your-life-depends-on-it-because-it-does-3794597">艾利什和她的兄弟芬尼斯公开支持哈里斯担任总统</a>。现在，在<a href="https://www.vogue.com/article/billie-eilish-november-2024-cover-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Vogue》杂志</em></a>发布的新封面聊天中（在代言之前就已经在进行中），艾利什开玩笑说她正在投票支持卡马拉。</p><p>艾利什在接受<em>《Vogue》杂志</em>采访时说道：“我的意思是，这也许是我们这个时代最重要的选举，而且很容易让人说，‘我不想考虑它......’。我也有同样的感觉：“我是一个人，我无法做出任何改变”。但事实是，我们都可以做出改变。我有这个平台，我会使用它。” </p><figure id="attachment_3763460" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3763460" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3763460" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270.jpg" alt="比莉·艾利什在舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3763460" class="wp-caption-text">比莉·艾利什.图片来源：阿图罗·霍姆斯/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>当被问及卡马拉承诺解决的与艾利什有关的问题时，这位年轻的音乐家回答道：“他真的是人权的忠实拥护者。非常支持妇女权利、妇女生殖权利、社会正义和枪支法。我的很多粉丝将第一次能够投票。所以我问，‘你喜欢自由吗？’第一位女总统？真的会很棒。作为一名女性，我希望在自己的国家感到安全。”</p><p>继上个月公开支持哈里斯之后，艾利什的《当派对结束时》最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilishs-when-the-partys-over-closes-kamala-harris-ad-on-reproductive-care-3795331">出现在民主党关于生殖保健的广告中</a>。</p><p>艾利什只是在即将到来的选举中表示支持哈里斯的众多音乐家之一。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">Taylor Swift</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-freedom-soundtracks-kamala-harris-first-presidential-election-campaign-video-3777987">Beyoncé</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-slams-those-avoiding-presidential-election-what-the-fuck-are-you-talking-about-3790934">Megan Thee Stallion</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-perform-what-about-us-with-daughter-to-close-democratic-national-convention-3786178">P!nk</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bon-iver-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-in-wisconsin-3781912">Bon Iver</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/quavo-backs-kamala-harris-for-tackling-gun-violence-at-atlanta-rally-3779672">Quavo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-endorses-kamala-harris-for-us-president-ive-only-got-one-vote-and-its-one-of-the-most-precious-possessions-that-i-have-3799537">Bruce Springsteen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-clears-up-elections-stance-im-voting-for-fucking-kamala-3797165">Chappell Roan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-throws-support-behind-kamala-harris-over-reproductive-rights-stance-3777706">Olivia Rodrigo</a>等艺术家也在今年 11 月的大选前站出来支持哈里斯。 </p><figure id="attachment_3777450" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3777450" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3777450" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="卡玛拉·哈里斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3777450" class="wp-caption-text">卡玛拉·哈里斯——图